node.text:
Excited to tell you about Ice's Whole Health journey! His happiness and wellbeing is so important to me and thanks to @Petco ’s accessible new approach, I'm learning about what he really needs when it comes to nutrition, exercise, mental health, and home health💛
For Ice's mental health, I've made sure he has a comfy space that puts him at ease, and for social health, I schedule lots of playtime with other dogs🐾Check out @Petco to level up your pet’s Whole Health routine! #Ad #Petco #IfweWerePets
